long_description: The thin and light LifeProof Fre Case preserves functionality and helps protect your iPhone 5s from water, dirt, snow and shock without adding a lot of bulk or weight. Case lets you use the home button's Touch ID function on your iPhone 5s. Fre shields your touch-screen under an ultra-flat, optically clear membrane; it's virtually invisible to the eye and touch, and almost invincible to the elements. Antireflective optical glass camera lens transforms your iPhone 5s into a colorful waterproof camera; sound enhancement system lets your capture quality audio.
